{"id":147869,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/04/当局证实格尔登寺冲突事件/","date":"2011-04-26T11:30:22Z","modified":"2011-04-26T11:30:22Z","title":"当局证实格尔登寺冲突事件","content":"<div>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">北京</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">据德新社报道，中国政府周二（4月26日）证实，四川阿坝州格尔登寺曾发生严重冲突事件。外交部一名发言人在例行记者会回答相关提问时表示，</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">“</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">少数僧侣长期破坏社会秩序</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">”</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，阿坝州地方政府对格尔登寺僧侣安排</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">“</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">集体法制教育</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">”</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。他称，采取这一措施是必要的，目的是为</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">“</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">维护正常宗教秩序</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">”</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。据流亡藏人组织的报告，在安全人员上周五夜间冲击格尔登寺的行动中，有两名平民丧生，到目前为止，已有300多名僧侣被强行送往一个不为外界所知的地方，参加</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">“</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">爱国主义教育运动</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">”</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。人权组织</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">“</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">自由西藏</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">”</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">对僧侣们的命运表示深切忧虑。上月中旬，格尔登寺一名年轻僧侣点火自焚，抗议当局。自焚死亡事件在寺内以及阿坝州引发骚乱。本月中旬，警方曾试图进入寺内，遭遇抵抗，未能成功。</span></p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGltcHJlc3Npb24iLCAicHJvcGVydGllcyI6IHsidG9rZW4iOiAiYTRhNDYwYTM5MDRlZWU4ZmY1ZTAyNGVhNGJkZTdhYzIifX0=&#038;ip=1&#038;img=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /><a href=\"http://fulltextrssfeed.com\"><img src=\"http://fulltextrssfeed.com/images/1x1.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"ftrf - full text rss\" /></a><a href=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGNsaWNrIiwgInByb3BlcnRpZXMiOiB7InRva2VuIjogImE0YTQ2MGEzOTA0ZWVlOGZmNWUwMjRlYTRiZGU3YWMyIn19&#038;ip=1&#038;redirect=http://talkita.com/wrap?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw-world.de%2Fdw%2Farticle%2F0%2C%2C15030030%2C00.html%3Fmaca%3Dchi-rss-chi-all-1127-rdf&#038;title=%E5%BD%93%E5%B1%80%E8%AF%81%E5%AE%9E%E6%A0%BC%E5%B0%94%E7%99%BB%E5%AF%BA%E5%86%B2%E7%AA%81%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6\">Chat about this story w/ Talkita</a></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[]}